+------------------------------+----------------------------+\line
                               |\line
                               v\line
+-----------------------------------------------------------+\line
| 4. Selecciona Zona / Area                                 |\line
+------------------------------+----------------------------+\line
                               |\line
                               v\line
+-----------------------------------------------------------+\line
| 5. Selecciona Sensor (codigo y descripcion)               |\line
+------------------------------+----------------------------+\line
                               |\line
                               v\line
+-----------------------------------------------------------+\line
